The alarm clock project with tkinter GUI.
it allows user to set an alarm and receive a notification when it goes off.

lesson learnt:
How to work with datetime module. Setting the specified alarm to synchronize with the current time
The sleep method is way to reset the time when the time changes, from sec to sec initially.
Threading, how to set a process in the background. The date time checker runs in the background and tries to evaluate the
set_alarm() and the alarm().
Using combobox. wonder how small boxes are created on various interfaces, well now I not only know but I can create them.
finally, loading a music file to an application. That's cool.

As the alarm says, Rise and shine!
